## Notes

- This packet is **not** a STIP application. It is a cycle-readiness
  diagnostic the lead agency uses to focus effort on candidates whose
  phase, fiscal-year, funding-source, and region placements can
  survive CTC and Caltrans district review before the full application
  package is assembled.
- Every programming row in this packet is mirrored as a
  `stip_programming_row` fact_block (plus one `stip_portfolio_summary`)
  appended to this run's `fact_blocks.jsonl`, so subsequent narrative
  and chat turns remain subject to the ClawModeler citation contract.

